Artists to include; @unknownblackfemale @twig.lips @stormritter @iamnarkita @chiara_collizzolli_veg @tinapsoinos_art @zafeiriamic @a.rosenyc

12 months, 4 seasons, a million walks of life & so many of our closest ones entering the spirit realm. 
I ended this tiny documentary with the largest, spirit I’ve ever known. 
9 months my favorite person in the world carried you, and no amount of social media really even matters but if you could touch every person who looked at this post and inspire the same light your eyes held, every day, you would change the world. 
We love you more than every star in the universe and back, you are the true beacon of love. We will teach the world like you taught us. ☀️
Shot by @brycepagter in Tulum
